  <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--border-top-5  ">Contact PCA</h2>


    <div class="organisation__contact-section organisation__contact-section--border-top">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--padding  ">General enquiries</h3>


    <div class="grid-row">
        <address class="column-half organisation__margin-bottom organisation__address">
            Pubs Code Adjudicator (enquiries)<br></br>Lower Ground<br></br>Victoria Square House<br></br>Victoria Square<br></br>Birmingham<br></br>B2 4AJ<br></br>United Kingdom<br></br>
        </address>

        <div class="column-half">

            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
                <p><a class="brand__color" href="https://www.rohs.bis.gov.uk/pca-enquiry/">Contact Form: General enquiries</a></p>
            </div>

            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
                <p>Telephone enquiry line</p>
                <p class="organisation__contact-number">0800 528 8080</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <p>The enquiry line is open: Monday to Thursday, 9:30am to 5pm and Friday, 9:30am to 4pm.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="organisation__contact-section organisation__contact-section--border-top">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--padding  ">Referrals</h3>


    <div class="grid-row">

        <div class="column-two-thirds">

            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
                <p><a class="brand__color" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/pubs-code-how-to-refer-an-issue-to-the-adjudicator/when-and-how-to-make-a-referral-to-the-pubs-code-adjudicator">Contact Form: Referrals</a></p>
            </div>

            <div class="organisation__margin-bottom">
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <p>There is a difference between a general enquiry and a formal referral to the PCA for arbitration. You can only make a referral if you are a tied tenant (or a pub owning business in relation to market rent only disputes), or authorised to act on their behalf.</p>
  </div>

</section>


